#: line_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"line_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id3155373\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select a curved line, and then click the <emph>Points </emph>icon on the <emph>Drawing</emph> Bar."
msgstr "ເລືອກເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງ, ແລ້ວຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ຈຸດ</emph> ໃນແຖບ <emph>ການແຕ້ມ</emph>."

#. 6p2a2
#: line_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"line_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id3156256\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <emph>Edit Points</emph> Bar, click the<emph> Insert Points</emph> icon."
msgstr "ໃນແຖບ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂຈຸດ</emph>, ໃຫ້ຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ແຊກຈຸດ</emph>."

#. m7aHh
#: line_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"line_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id3083280\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the line where you want to add the point, and drag a short distance."
msgstr "ຄລິກໃສ່ເສັ້ນບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການເພີ່ມຈຸດ, ແລ້ວລາກໄປເປັນໄລຍະທາງສັ້ນໆ."

#. QKtb3
#: line_edit.xhp
msgctxt ""
"line_edit.xhp\n"
"par_id3154643\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If a data point does not have a control point, select the data point, and then click the <emph>Convert to Curve</emph> icon on the <emph>Edit Points</emph> Bar."
msgstr "ຖ້າຈຸດຂໍ້ມູນບໍ່ມີຈຸດຄວບຄຸມ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຈຸດຂໍ້ມູນນັ້ນ ແລ້ວຄລິກໄອຄອນ <emph>ແປງເປັນເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງ</emph> ໃນແຖບ <emph>ແກ້ໄຂຈຸດ</emph>."

#. STteE
