"presenter_console.xhp\n"
"hd_id181512827240072\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Normal Mode"
msgstr "ໂໝດປົກກະຕິ"

#. pCQCq
#: presenter_console.xhp
msgctxt ""
"presenter_console.xhp\n"
"par_id341512828780413\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The Normal mode shows the current slide on the left and the next slide on the right of the computer display."
msgstr "ໂໝດປົກກະຕິຈະສະແດງສະໄລ້ປັດຈຸບັນຢູ່ເບື້ອງຊ້າຍ ແລະ ສະໄລ້ຖັດໄປຢູ່ເບື້ອງຂວາຂອງໜ້າຈໍຄອມພິວເຕີ."

#. hRYrF
